<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.4.6">
<l>mārvil tiruvaṉ valaṉēntu cakkarattaṉ</l>
<l>pāraip piḷanta paramaṉ parañcōti</l>
<l>kāril tikaḻkāyā vaṇṇaṉ katirmuṭimēl</l>
<l>tāril naṟuntuḻāy tāḻntūtāy kōltumpī.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Twiggy dragonfly, alight and sip the fragrant tulasī in the garland</l>
<l>On the shining crown of the one with Tiru on his chest,</l>
<l>The one with the discus held on the right,</l>
<l rend="indent">the supreme who gouged open the earth,</l>
<l>The heavenly splendor, the one the color of kāyā buds sparkling in the rain.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
